<http://www.spektrix.com/tidemarktheatre/event/56601ACCRKSPGKVDGHVRNMKGTVPHPQPBK>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Love Can Build A Bridge";
  schema:description """
	Love Can Build a Bridge is a heartfelt tribute celebrating the timeless music, harmonies, and spirit of The Judds and Wynonna. Starring Jona Kristinsson as Wynonna and Allison Barlow as Naomi, this powerful show brings audiences on a journey through the unforgettable songs that helped define generations of country music fans.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Featuring beloved hits such as “Grandpa (Tell Me ’Bout the Good Old Days),” “Mama He’s Crazy,” “Why Not Me,” and “Love Can Build a Bridge,” the production captures both the heartwarming family connection of The Judds and the soulful powerhouse vocals of Wynonna’s solo career.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Backed by professional live musicians and rich storytelling, Love Can Build a Bridge delivers an emotional, high-energy evening of music, memories, and classic country magic. From touching ballads to foot-stomping favorites, this tribute honors the legacy of one of country music’s most iconic family duos.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://youtu.be/Xft4YqffQ8M\">https://youtu.be/Xft4YqffQ8M</a><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Tickets: $53.00 Admission <span class=\"ItalicText\">(+applicable taxes & fees)</span>
""";
