<http://www.spektrix.com/tidemarktheatre/event/59201ANQRMQQHPMKRBHKNCGQLPCVGCBKN>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "The Great Canadian Road Trip";
  schema:description """
	Bringing together three of the country's most beloved performers - <span class=\"BoldText\">Doc Walker</span>, <span class=\"BoldText\">Jason McCoy</span>, and <span class=\"BoldText\">Michelle Wright</span> - this unique concert experience blends chart-topping hits, behind-the-scenes stories, and the moments that shaped their remarkable careers. More than a concert, it's an evening of music, memories, and laughter shared by artists who have helped define the soundtrack of Canadian country music for generations.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Award-winning duo Doc Walker have spent nearly three decades topping charts and winning fans across the country with their signature blend of heartfelt songwriting and crowd-pleasing energy. Joining them is Jason McCoy, one of Canada's most recognizable country entertainers, whose career spans more than 35 years as both a solo artist and frontman of The Road Hammers. Rounding out this powerhouse lineup is Canadian Country Music Hall of Fame inductee Michelle Wright, whose trailblazing career helped open international doors for Canadian country artists and produced some of the genre's most enduring songs.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Together, these legendary performers will take audiences on a musical journey across decades of Canadian country music, sharing the stories behind the songs and celebrating the friendships, experiences, and fans that have made the ride worthwhile.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Whether you've been listening to these artists for years or are discovering their music for the first time, The Great Canadian Road Trip Tour promises an evening of exceptional music, unforgettable stories, and a rare opportunity to see three Canadian country icons sharing one stage.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Tickets: $57.00 Admission <span class=\"ItalicText\">(+applicable taxes & fees)</span>
""";
  schema:startDate "2026-10-21T19:30:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
